OverHistory.Commentry: Jaydev Unadkat bowling to MS Dhoni, full toss ball, outside leg stump, MS Dhoni plays an aggressive front foot flick for 4 runs
OverHistory.UPDCommentry: MAHI MAAR RAHA HAI! Jaydev Unadkat bowling to MS Dhoni, full toss ball, outside leg stump, MS Dhoni clips this off his pads and the ball runs away to the deep square leg boundary and Chennai Super Kings win by 3 wickets to get their second win of the campaign!
